Description: Cross Academy has day and evening students, but the latter have a secret: they are vampires.

Description: Life in a high school filled with werewolves and vampires continues.
Title: ROSARIO+VAMPIRE: SEASON II, VOL. 6

Description: This series is about grade-school boys who want to become professionals in the manga industry. In this installment, when their series begins to lose popularity, will it be cancelled?

Title: POKEMON ADVENTURES: DIAMOND AND PEARL/PLATINUM, VOL. 3

Title: BLUE EXORCIST, VOL. 4
